      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THUNDER ROSE (6) fast out of the inside draw with a slick early sectional and clocking 22.58 in a 1.5 lengths win at this track over 400m last time. Looks to have an edge on most of these. BEAR THE BRUNT (1) goes very well this course and distance starting seven times for three wins and two minors. Hit the frame latest (22.94) when second at this track in a Mix 3/4. With even luck and a clean start should be around the money. BUFFALO COWBOY (2) latest effort finished 3rd in a Grade 5 on March 13 over 435m at Sale behind Holly Rose beaten 4 lengths (24.70). Looks one of the chances. PRETTY PIPA (3) racing over this course and distance brings the best out in her.",
